						 <p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/damnce" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5390805&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561103235" alt="DAMNCE" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5390805)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/damnce" >DAMNCE</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thebluehour" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4078000&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561103235" alt="TheBlueHour" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4078000)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thebluehour" >TheBlueHour</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/floppyphoenix" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561103235" alt="FloppyPhoenix" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/floppyphoenix" >FloppyPhoenix</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nameless-mediocre" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4176498&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561103235" alt="Nameless Mediocre" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4176498)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nameless-mediocre" >Nameless Mediocre</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/oboebandgeek99" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1782920&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561103235" alt="Oboebandgeek99" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1782920)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/oboebandgeek99" >Oboebandgeek99</a></span>, and others for reading and suggestions, and especially <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/damnce" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5390805&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561103235" alt="DAMNCE" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5390805)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/damnce" >DAMNCE</a></span> for enthusiasm.</p> <p>This is also for <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmagnus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=318209&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561103235" alt="DrMagnus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=318209)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmagnus" >DrMagnus</a></span>'s contest.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">[+]&nbsp;Notes&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;name</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">[-]&nbsp;Notes&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;name</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <ul> <li>In GSC, the Lake of Rage was subject to radio waves from Mahagony town that forced its magikarp to evolve.</li> <li>Gyarados is similar appearance to Chinese dragons, which in itself is a symbol of Chinese imperial power.</li> <li>A Red Gyarados, is, therefore, a <em>Red</em> Chinese Dragon, born from the Lake of Rage.</li> <li>Lake Hong is one of the places where the original <em>Red</em> guerrillas started.</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
